description: Nice beer garden on Vyšehrad

name: Na Pošte
description: Place of my youth

name: U Staré pošty
description: My favorite stop on way home

description: I ve lived nearby for 7 years,  now after more than 10 years it's still the same -incredible.

name: U Valtrů
description: Cool village pub
